Class MolCountTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.db.MolCountTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QuestionConstants, XMLConstants, Serializable

    class MolCountTable
extends Object
implements QuestionConstants, Serializable
    Holds lists of String representations of molecules retrieved from the log file and their number of occurrences.
